{
  "stem": "14810.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And here you have those-- you work outdoors with this little jacket and no-- most of them, just so many of them, literally froze to death.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Many of them just contracted pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you know, Auschwitz, if you got sick, the only way, the only solution is for you to die because they didn't give you any medication.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Also the water-- the water was also very polluted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It wasn't purified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember from the beginning, the inmates told us to not drink the water-- the older ones who were there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for a while we didn't drink the water, but after a while you can't help yourself and you start drink the water.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many of us got diarrhea, and diarrhea was a killer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a killer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, with no medication and you couldn't hold even the little food they gave you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't hold in it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you start to lose weight and became a Muselmann.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They call it-- Muselmann was the expression, skeleton.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And once you became a skeleton, you can't work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had no use for you, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you knew it's just a matter of time, and Mengele used to come in for inspection, selections, right into the barracks every few weeks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to get rid of the sick ones, the weak ones who cannot perform anymore to make room for the new ones.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to undress ourselves naked, stark naked in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to stay before him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to turn around and stoop over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if he noticed the bones sticking out, that was your death sentence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took him number down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we all had numbers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took the boys and locked them up in the next room.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
